# Payment & Billing

## Overview
Build a production-ready Payment & Billing subsystem for Archject that enables subscription management, billing, invoices, and add-on purchases via Stripe. The system will support seat-based or usage-based billing, proration, webhooks for real-time events, and an admin UI for managing invoices, refunds, and plan changes. The feature set includes a secure checkout flow, an order/history view with downloadable receipts, and a subscription management page with payment method updates and plan upgrades/downgrades. All billing data must be stored securely with Stripe as the source of truth for payment data. No raw card data should be stored on our servers; leverage Stripe Elements / Payment Intents and Stripe Customer objects. Provide a polished, accessible, mobile-first UI aligned to the project’s design system.

---

## Components to Build

- [Stripe (Payments & Billing) API Integration]
  - Create and manage Stripe Customers, Payment Methods, Subscriptions, Invoices, and Payment Intents.
  - Implement webhooks for events: invoice.created, invoice.payment_succeeded/failed,customer.subscription.updated, invoice.finalized, charge.refunded, invoice.upcoming, etc.
  - Support add-ons as line items in subscriptions or standalone invoices.
  - Implement usage-based metering (subscribable seats, meters) with usage records sent to Stripe for metered billing.
  - Implement proration logic for plan changes (upgrade/downgrade) with prorations applied in invoices.
  - Securely store Stripe metadata on user records (customer_id, subscription_id, default_payment_method_id, invoice_history_ref, etc.).

- [Frontend: Checkout / Payment Page]
  - Secure, PCI-compliant checkout flow using Stripe Elements or Payment Intents.
  - Order Summary showing selected plan, add-ons, quantities, pricing, taxes if applicable.
  - Coupon entry with validation and Stripe-compatible discount handling.
  - Securely collect payment details without storing card data on server.
  - Real-time validation, error handling, and success flows with receipts.

- [Frontend: Transaction / Order History Page]
  - List past payments, invoices, subscription events with filters (date range, status, plan, add-ons).
  - Downloadable receipts/invoices (PDF or Stripe-hosted invoice link).
  - Search, sort, and export capabilities (CSV/JSON).
  - Status indicators (paid, due, past_due, refunded).

- [Frontend: Billing / Subscription Page]
  - View current subscription, invoices, upcoming invoices, and usage metrics.
  - Update payment methods (set default method, remove method, add new method via Stripe).
  - Upgrade/D downgrade plans and add-ons with prorated billing preview.
  - Visual cues for status (active, trial, past_due, canceled).
  - Admin-only controls for refunds, manual invoice adjustments, and plan changes with proration.

- [Admin UI Components]
  - Invoice management: view, refund, void, adjust line items, apply credits.
  - Plan changes with proration details and audit trail.
