  - Usage metering: app sends usage events to Stripe as needed; reflect in invoices via metered billing.
  - Webhooks: Stripe events update local records; trigger user-facing notifications (receipts, payment success/failure, subscription changes).
  - Admin actions: refunds or adjustments propagate to Stripe and update local invoices.

- Data mapping
  - Map Stripe objects to local models: customer -> user, subscription -> subscription, invoice -> invoice, payment_method -> user.payment_methods, plan/add-on prices -> Stripe price IDs.

